<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"><meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<title>智储优控 · 提交材料导览｜2026 ABB 杯智能仓储赛题</title>
<style>
:root{
  --abb:#ff000f;--ink:#1a1d21;--muted:#5c6670;--faint:#8a939c;
  --line:#dde2e8;--soft:#f4f6f8;--bg:#eef1f4;--paper:#ffffff;
  --navy:#17365d;--navy2:#3f628f;--green:#1e7a4d;--amber:#9a6b00;
  --rail:236px;--evidence:304px;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box}
html,body{width:100%;height:100%;margin:0}
body{min-width:1080px;min-height:640px;height:100vh;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg);color:var(--ink);
  font-family:"Microsoft YaHei","PingFang SC","Segoe UI",system-ui,sans-serif;
  display:flex;flex-direction:column}
button,a{font:inherit}button{color:inherit}
.topline{height:5px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--abb) 0 9%,var(--ink) 9%)}

/* ── 品牌栏 ── */
.masthead{height:58px;background:var(--paper);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 22px;gap:18px}
.brand{font:700 17px/1 Georgia,"Songti SC","SimSun",serif;white-space:nowrap;letter-spacing:.5px}
.brand i{font:900 19px Arial;color:var(--abb);font-style:normal;margin-right:9px}
.docline{color:var(--faint);font:11px/1.4 "Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;border-left:1px solid var(--line);padding-left:16px}
.docline b{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-weight:600;font-size:12px}
.masthead .scope{margin-left:auto;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:12px}
.scope span{font-size:12px;color:var(--muted)}
.scope b{font:600 11.5px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--green);border:1px solid #a9cdb9;background:#f1faf5;padding:5px 10px;border-radius:3px}

/* ── 指标带 ── */
.metric-ribbon{background:var(--paper);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.15fr repeat(4,1fr);padding:12px 22px 14px;gap:14px}
.metric{min-width:0;padding:2px 0 0 12px;border-left:3px solid #b9c2cb}
.metric.primary{border-left-color:var(--abb)}
.metric .value{display:block;font:700 21px/1.15 Consolas,"JetBrains Mono",monospace;color:var(--navy);white-space:nowrap}
.metric .label{display:block;margin-top:4px;color:var(--muted);font-size:11.5px;white-space:nowrap;overflow:hidden;text-overflow:ellipsis}
.metric .cal{display:inline-block;margin-top:3px;font:600 10px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--green);background:#f1faf5;border:1px solid #cde4d6;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:3px}

/* ── 三栏工作区 ── */
.workspace{flex:1;min-height:0;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:var(--rail) minmax(520px,1fr) var(--evidence);gap:12px;padding:12px 16px}
.rail,.reader,.evidence-rail{min-height:0;background:var(--paper);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px}

/* 左栏 */
.rail{display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:16px 15px 12px;overflow:hidden}
.rail-kicker{font:700 10px/1 Consolas,monospace;color:var(--abb);letter-spacing:2px}
.rail h1{font:700 21px/1.2 Georgia,"Songti SC","SimSun",serif;margin:8px 0 6px}
.rail .intro{font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--muted);margin:0 0 12px}
.progress-meta{display:flex;justify-content:space-between;font:11px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--faint)}
.progress{height:3px;background:#e6eaee;margin:6px 0 13px;border-radius:2px}
.progress i{display:block;height:100%;background:var(--abb);transition:.22s;border-radius:2px}
.chapter-nav{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:4px}
.chapter-nav button{min-height:40px;border:0;border-left:3px solid transparent;background:var(--paper);
  text-align:left;padding:6px 9px;cursor:pointer;display:grid;grid-template-columns:27px 1fr;align-items:center;border-radius:0 3px 3px 0}
.chapter-nav button:hover{background:var(--soft)}
.chapter-nav button[aria-selected="true"]{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;border-left-color:var(--abb)}
.chapter-nav .no{font:11px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--faint)}
.chapter-nav button[aria-selected="true"] .no{color:#ff8a92}
.chapter-nav .name{font-size:13px;font-weight:650}
.rail-tip{margin-top:auto;border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:9px;color:var(--faint);font-size:10px;line-height:1.55}

/* 中栏 */
.reader{display:grid;grid-template-rows:42px minmax(0,1fr);overflow:hidden}
.readerbar{border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;gap:10px;background:#fbfcfd}
.crumb{font:11.5px "Microsoft YaHei",sans-serif;color:var(--muted)}
.crumb b{color:var(--ink)}
.next{margin-left:auto;border:1px solid var(--ink);background:var(--ink);color:#fff;padding:7px 14px;font-size:11.5px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px}
.next:hover{background:#33383e}
.page-stack{min-height:0;position:relative}
.chapter{height:100%;overflow:auto;padding:22px 26px 20px;scrollbar-width:thin}
.chapter[hidden]{display:none}
.eyebrow{font:700 10px/1 Consolas,monospace;letter-spacing:1.8px;color:var(--faint)}
.chapter h2{font:700 clamp(24px,2.4vw,34px)/1.12 Georgia,"Songti SC","SimSun",serif;margin:8px 0 10px;letter-spacing:-.3px}
.lede{max-width:780px;font:15px/1.75 Georgia,"Songti SC","SimSun",serif;color:#2c3238;margin:0 0 16px}
.rule-title{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin:16px 0 10px;font-size:12.5px;font-weight:700;color:var(--muted)}
.rule-title:after{content:"";height:1px;background:var(--line);flex:1}

/* 00 意图卡 */
.intent-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px}
.intent{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper);min-height:104px;text-align:left;padding:14px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:4px;transition:.12s}
.intent:hover{border-color:var(--ink);box-shadow:0 2px 8px rgba(23,25,28,.08)}
.intent .tag{font:700 10px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--abb);letter-spacing:1px}
.intent b{display:block;font:700 16px Georgia,"SimSun",serif;margin:6px 0 5px}
.intent span{display:block;font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--muted)}
.system-strip{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);border:1px solid var(--line);margin-top:12px;border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.system-strip div{padding:11px 12px;border-right:1px solid var(--line);min-width:0;background:var(--paper)}
.system-strip div:last-child{border-right:0}
.system-strip b{display:block;font-size:12px}
.system-strip span{font-size:10px;color:var(--faint);display:block;margin-top:2px}
.route-note{margin-top:12px;background:var(--soft);border-left:3px solid var(--navy);padding:11px 14px;font-size:12.5px;color:#39424b;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0}
.route-note b{color:var(--navy)}

/* 01 结果卡 */
.result-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:11px}
.result-card{border:1px solid var(--line);padding:15px 16px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--paper);
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr auto;gap:6px 12px;align-items:end}
.result-card b{font:700 27px/1 Consolas,monospace;color:var(--navy)}
.result-card h3{font:700 13.5px Georgia,"SimSun",serif;margin:0}
.result-card p{grid-column:1/-1;font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--muted);margin:2px 0 0}
.result-card .cal{font:600 10px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--green);background:#f1faf5;border:1px solid #cde4d6;padding:1px 6px;border-radius:3px;white-space:nowrap}
.evidence-band{margin-top:11px;padding:12px 14px;background:var(--soft);border-left:3px solid var(--navy);
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.15fr 1fr 1fr;gap:14px;border-radius:0 4px 4px 0}
.evidence-band b{font-size:11.5px}
.evidence-band span{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:10.5px;line-height:1.55;margin-top:3px}

/* 02 方法 */
.method-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.1fr .9fr;gap:12px}
.method-flow{border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.method-step{display:grid;grid-template-columns:30px 1fr;gap:9px;padding:11px 13px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper)}
.method-step:last-child{border-bottom:0}
.method-step i{font:700 11px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--abb);font-style:normal;padding-top:2px}
.method-step b{font-size:12.5px}
.method-step small{display:block;color:var(--muted);font-size:11px;margin-top:2px;line-height:1.5}
.fact-sheet{background:var(--ink);color:#fff;padding:15px;border-radius:4px}
.fact-sheet h3{font:700 15px Georgia,"SimSun",serif;margin:0 0 9px}
.fact-sheet dl{margin:0}
.fact-sheet div{display:grid;grid-template-columns:82px 1fr;border-top:1px solid #ffffff22;padding:8px 0}
.fact-sheet dt{font:600 10.5px Consolas,monospace;color:#aeb7c0}
.fact-sheet dd{margin:0;font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.5}

/* 03 HMI */
.hmi-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:10px}
.hmi{border:1px solid var(--line);padding:14px;min-height:126px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--paper)}
.hmi .p{font:700 10.5px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--abb);letter-spacing:.5px}
.hmi h3{font:700 15px Georgia,"SimSun",serif;margin:6px 0}
.hmi p{font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--muted);margin:0}
.control-proof{margin-top:11px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:126px 1fr;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:4px;overflow:hidden}
.control-proof strong{background:var(--navy);color:#fff;display:grid;place-items:center;font:700 26px Consolas,monospace}
.control-proof div{padding:12px 14px;background:var(--paper)}
.control-proof b{font-size:12.5px}
.control-proof p{font-size:11.5px;color:var(--muted);margin:4px 0 0;line-height:1.6}

/* 04 物理与边界 */
.compare{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 40px 1fr;align-items:stretch}
.compare-card{border:1px solid var(--line);padding:15px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--paper)}
.compare-card h3{font:700 16px Georgia,"SimSun",serif;margin:5px 0 8px}
.compare-card p{font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.65;color:var(--muted);margin:0}
.compare-card .big{font:700 24px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--navy)}
.compare .bridge{display:grid;place-items:center;font:bold 18px Georgia;color:var(--faint)}
.boundary-box{margin-top:12px;border:1px solid #e4d9be;background:#fdfaf2;padding:12px 14px;border-radius:4px;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:112px 1fr;gap:14px}
.boundary-box b{font:700 13.5px Georgia,"SimSun",serif;color:var(--amber)}
.boundary-box p{font-size:11.5px;line-height:1.65;color:#5a5648;margin:0}

/* 05 模块 */
.module-layout{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.35fr .65fr;gap:12px}
.module-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:7px}
.module{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper);text-align:left;padding:9px 11px;min-height:56px;cursor:pointer;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:28px 1fr;align-items:center;border-radius:4px}
.module:hover,.module.selected{border-color:var(--ink);background:var(--soft)}
.module .id{font:700 11px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--navy)}
.module b{display:block;font-size:12px}
.module small{display:block;font-size:9.5px;margin-top:2px;color:var(--faint)}
.module small.ok{color:var(--green)}
.module-detail{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--ink);color:#fff;padding:15px;border-radius:4px}
.module-detail .id{font:600 10px Consolas,monospace;color:#ff858d}
.module-detail h3{font:700 16px Georgia,"SimSun",serif;margin:7px 0}
.module-detail p{font-size:11px;line-height:1.65;color:#c2c8ce}
.module-detail b{display:block;border-top:1px solid #ffffff26;padding-top:9px;margin-top:9px;font-size:11px;color:#fff}

/* 06 材料 */
.material-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:8px}
.material-row{border:1px solid var(--line);background:var(--paper);text-align:left;padding:11px 12px;min-height:76px;cursor:pointer;
  display:grid;grid-template-columns:34px 1fr;gap:8px;border-radius:4px}
.material-row:hover,.material-row.selected{border-color:var(--ink);background:var(--soft)}
.material-row .id{font:700 11px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--abb)}
.material-row b{font:700 13px Georgia,"SimSun",serif}
.material-row span span{display:block;font-size:10.5px;line-height:1.5;color:var(--muted);margin-top:3px}

/* 右栏 */
.evidence-rail{display:flex;flex-direction:column;padding:17px 16px 13px;overflow:hidden}
.ev-kicker{font:700 10px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--abb);letter-spacing:1.6px}
.evidence-rail h2{font:700 19px/1.25 Georgia,"Songti SC","SimSun",serif;margin:8px 0}
.caliber{align-self:flex-start;border:1px solid #b6bec6;padding:4px 8px;font:600 10px Consolas,monospace;color:var(--muted);border-radius:3px}
.claim{font:12.5px/1.7 Georgia,"Songti SC","SimSun",serif;margin:11px 0;color:#333a41}
.ev-block{border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:10px;margin-top:3px}
.ev-block b{display:block;font-size:10.5px;margin-bottom:6px;color:var(--muted)}
.ev-block pre{white-space:pre-wrap;word-break:break-word;background:var(--soft);border:1px solid #e2e6ea;margin:0;padding:9px;font:10.5px/1.55 Consolas,monospace;color:#39424b;border-radius:3px}
.ev-block p{font-size:11px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--muted);margin:0}
.context-actions{margin-top:10px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);padding-top:10px;display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:7px}
.context-actions[hidden]{display:none}
.context-actions a,.context-actions button{border:1px solid var(--ink);text-align:center;text-decoration:none;padding:8px 5px;font-size:10.5px;cursor:pointer;border-radius:3px}
.context-actions a{background:var(--ink);color:#fff}
.context-actions button{background:var(--paper)}
.evidence-foot{margin-top:auto;padding-top:9px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);font:10px/1.6 Consolas,"Microsoft YaHei",monospace;color:var(--faint)}

/* 底栏 */
.statusbar{height:30px;background:var(--ink);color:#c7cdd3;display:flex;align-items:center;padding:0 16px;gap:14px;font:10px Consolas,"Microsoft YaHei",monospace}
.statusbar b{color:#fff}
.statusbar span:last-child{margin-left:auto;color:#ff8b92}
#toast{position:fixed;left:50%;bottom:40px;transform:translateX(-50%);background:var(--ink);color:#fff;padding:8px 14px;font-size:11px;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:.18s;z-index:50;border-radius:4px}

@media(max-width:1180px){:root{--rail:212px;--evidence:278px}.workspace{gap:8px;padding-left:8px;padding-right:8px}.chapter{padding-left:17px;padding-right:17px}.metric-ribbon{padding-left:12px;padding-right:12px}.metric .value{font-size:17px}}
@media(max-height:780px){.rail .intro{display:none}.rail h1{font-size:19px;margin:7px 0 8px}.chapter-nav button{min-height:35px;padding:4px 9px}.progress{margin-bottom:10px}.rail-tip{display:none}.metric-ribbon{padding-top:9px;padding-bottom:10px}.metric .value{font-size:18px}}
@media(max-width:980px){body{min-width:0;min-height:0;height:auto;display:block;overflow:auto}.metric-ribbon{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.workspace{height:auto;grid-template-columns:1fr;padding:10px}.rail,.reader,.evidence-rail{min-height:auto}.chapter-nav{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}.rail-tip{display:none}.reader{min-height:640px}.evidence-rail{min-height:400px}.statusbar{display:none}.intent-grid,.hmi-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}.method-grid,.module-layout{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="topline"></div>

<header class="masthead">
  <div class="brand"><i>ABB</i>智储优控</div>
  <div class="docline"><b>提交材料导览 · 评审工作台</b>2026 ABB 杯 · 智能仓储赛题 · 初赛与决赛材料合并提交</div>
  <div class="scope"><span>建议阅读:总览 90 秒 · 全程 8 分钟</span><b>● 全部结论附口径与来源</b></div>
</header>

<section class="metric-ribbon" aria-label="全局关键指标">
  <div class="metric primary"><span class="value">8.17 ± 0.67 s</span><span class="label">期望取货时间 · 30-seed 泛化主证</span><span class="cal">sim · H 口径 · n=30</span></div>
  <div class="metric"><span class="value">−61.6%</span><span class="label">较顺序基线降幅 · 30/30 seed 正收益</span><span class="cal">sim</span></div>
  <div class="metric"><span class="value">75 / 0</span><span class="label">控制器在线自测 · 断言通过/失败</span><span class="cal">AB PC 仿真</span></div>
  <div class="metric"><span class="value">98.5% / 99.19%</span><span class="label">算法选择 oracle 达成率 · 双口径</span><span class="cal">sim · 390 可比实例</span></div>
  <div class="metric"><span class="value">9 / 9</span><span class="label">Factory I/O 全链取放运行成功</span><span class="cal">54 格 · 技术预演</span></div>
</section>

<div class="workspace">

<aside class="rail">
  <div class="rail-kicker">2026 ABB CUP · SUBMISSION GUIDE</div>
  <h1>提交材料导览</h1>
  <p class="intro">这不是目录堆叠,而是一条「结论 → 方法 → 控制 → 物理 → 展示 → 复现」的有限阅读路径。每一章的右侧,始终显示当前结论的口径、来源与边界。</p>
  <div class="progress-meta"><span id="progressText">01 / 07</span><span id="progressName">首读总览</span></div>
  <div class="progress"><i id="progressFill" style="width:14.285%"></i></div>
  <nav class="chapter-nav" role="tablist" aria-orientation="vertical" aria-label="导览章节">
    <button role="tab" id="tab-overview" aria-controls="panel-overview" aria-selected="true" data-id="overview"><span class="no">00</span><span class="name">首读总览</span></button>
    <button role="tab" id="tab-results" aria-controls="panel-results" aria-selected="false" data-id="results" tabindex="-1"><span class="no">01</span><span class="name">核心结论</span></button>
    <button role="tab" id="tab-method" aria-controls="panel-method" aria-selected="false" data-id="method" tabindex="-1"><span class="no">02</span><span class="name">模型与算法</span></button>
    <button role="tab" id="tab-control" aria-controls="panel-control" aria-selected="false" data-id="control" tabindex="-1"><span class="no">03</span><span class="name">控制与 HMI</span></button>
    <button role="tab" id="tab-physical" aria-controls="panel-physical" aria-selected="false" data-id="physical" tabindex="-1"><span class="no">04</span><span class="name">物理验证与边界</span></button>
    <button role="tab" id="tab-modules" aria-controls="panel-modules" aria-selected="false" data-id="modules" tabindex="-1"><span class="no">05</span><span class="name">可视化展示体系</span></button>
    <button role="tab" id="tab-materials" aria-controls="panel-materials" aria-selected="false" data-id="materials" tabindex="-1"><span class="no">06</span><span class="name">材料与复现</span></button>
  </nav>
  <div class="rail-tip">键盘 ↑↓ 切换章节 · Home/End 跳转<br>本页单文件离线可开,无外部依赖。</div>
</aside>

<main class="reader">
  <div class="readerbar"><span class="crumb">智储优控 / <b id="crumb">首读总览</b></span><button class="next" id="nextChapter" type="button">下一章 · 核心结论 →</button></div>
  <div class="page-stack">

  <section class="chapter" role="tabpanel" id="panel-overview" aria-labelledby="tab-overview">
    <div class="eyebrow">READING START · 约 90 秒</div>
    <h2>先判断作品解决了什么,再决定深入哪一层。</h2>
    <p class="lede">面向单巷道、单堆垛机的 20 列 × 20 层自动化立体仓库,本作品以可复现的运动学与约束模型为底座,用 AWRA-LS 与策略库优化货位分配,把核心逻辑落实为 ABB AC500 Structured Text 与三页制 HMI,并以 Factory I/O 代表性物理场景完成动作链技术预演——四层验证各自独立、口径分离、全部可复现。</p>
    <div class="rule-title">按评审意图进入</div>
    <div class="intent-grid">
      <button class="intent" data-route="results"><span class="tag">01 · OUTCOME</span><b>先看结论</b><span>四个关键数字,四种不同证据角色:泛化主证、控制器测试、算法选择、物理预演。</span></button>
      <button class="intent" data-route="control"><span class="tag">03 · ENGINEERING</span><b>先看工程</b><span>直接检查 ST 控制实现、75/0 证据级别与三页 HMI 的频率-风险分层。</span></button>
      <button class="intent" data-route="materials"><span class="tag">06 · REPRODUCE</span><b>直接查证</b><span>从结论跳到命令、文件与一键复现入口,每个数字都可回源。</span></button>
    </div>
    <div class="system-strip" aria-label="系统五阶段">
